org.beryx.streamplify.product

Class BigIntegerCartesianProduct

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.beryx.streamplify.BigIntegerIndexedSpliterator<int[],BigIntegerCartesianProduct>
      • org.beryx.streamplify.product.BigIntegerCartesianProduct
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Spliterator<int[]>, Streamable<int[],BigIntegerCartesianProduct>

    public class BigIntegerCartesianProduct
extends BigIntegerIndexedSpliterator<int[],BigIntegerCartesianProduct>
    Provides streams of cartesian product tuples.
    When the cardinality of the cartesian product can fit in a long, you may consider using the more efficient LongCartesianProduct.
